      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD]{Mechanic Trick}</p>\n<p>As a standard action, you can temporarily patch up a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.2sVSvaOrr3uLW8Uq]{broken weapon} or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.o8MNHcDmjahBNydI]{technological} item to suppress the penalties from the broken condition for 1 minute per mechanic level. This does not restore any Hit Points to the item, and it does not function on an item reduced to 0 Hit Points. Additionally, when filling the engineer role during starship combat, once per combat you can perform the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.starship-actions.Item.B9CsbXIcE9ZGlGv9]{Hold It Together} action in the same round you perform another engineering action.</p>"
